<br>
You will not get a faction hit if you only send in pet.  As someone pointed out, the AA pets do give you a faction hit.  I buffed my pet during a fight to see if that would give me a faction hit, but I can't remember if it did or not, lol.  I'm thinking it did though.<br>
<br>
What I do is just send in pet.  I don't nuke unless it seems like it's going to be close.  I hate doing faction work.  It's a waste of time that I don't have, so the less hits I get, the better.<br>
